{"id": 2014, "genre": 1001, "title": "日常里，你都有过哪些小型人设崩塌时刻？", "description": "你在网络上，在伴侣面前、朋友面前、父母前面、同事上司面前，都扮演过什么样的自己？有过什么样的原形毕露时刻？（题图来自：Wikimedia Commons）", "record_count": 2772, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171114174235UFzKpqyl8vd3t9Nc.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-17T03:00:29Z", "options": [{"id": 264704, "content": "以前对谁都装，对父母都要伪装。本来，以为终于遇到一个不用伪装的人，后来发现不伪装的自己没人喜欢，所以，还是继续套上壳装着乖巧善良。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853433}, {"id": 249602, "content": "朋友圈忘记屏蔽，被同事看到我朋友圈晒的手表和钢笔，不能再装穷了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186479}, {"id": 249859, "content": "爸妈对外一直宣称我是勤俭持家，不爱花钱。。。实际上每个月零食一堆，还有不定期从淘宝上买来一些实际没啥用的小玩意\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997083}, {"id": 249604, "content": "老大因为看到我经常在公司走廊上摩擦摩擦，突然反应过来原来我是个神经病。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1153111}, {"id": 249605, "content": "我一边要压抑着自己悲观的情绪和想法，一边让自己看起来开朗活泼人见人爱，就像个神经病，却无力改变这种模式。", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186522}, {"id": 249607, "content": "当我对一个人特别不耐烦的时候平时维持的好形象全崩了", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186526}, {"id": 249608, "content": "楼上超过十位数需要计算器的那位 超过十位数 大部分人都需要计算器吧 哈哈哈哈哈?", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 426356}, {"id": 249609, "content": "插上数据线下意识点了信任，就低头发信息，女同事看见图册里的私照，纯情少年的人设瞬间红脸崩塌。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186533}, {"id": 249866, "content": "就在外人面前装傻卖萌，然后事后只想锤死自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1153250}, {"id": 254731, "content": "没有人设", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086674}, {"id": 249613, "content": "突然无意卖萌打破高冷形象。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182272}, {"id": 249616, "content": "在男朋友面前一直想做纯情仙女，有一次一起出去旅游的时候吃坏肚子不停放屁，真的有种想分手的冲动", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136589}, {"id": 249617, "content": "是因为薛之谦才会提出这种问题的吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026536}, {"id": 249618, "content": "表面大大咧咧，内心敏感，对男生就是没事没事我自己来，心里却很期待", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797049}, {"id": 249874, "content": "做自己", "image": "img/option/option/20171120130300yqTRNl7PpdbxS3QL.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 406438}, {"id": 249619, "content": "收到前男友请柬", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886463}, {"id": 249620, "content": "鼻毛……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335095}, {"id": 249621, "content": "哈哈小时候看了射雕英雄传，学习郭靖一直很耿直，活的比较自由，不在意别人看法的路过，所以人设没崩过", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1167652}, {"id": 249627, "content": "一个高中顶级学霸，上了大学考试才30分，现在正在颓废中", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1158243}, {"id": 249631, "content": "偷懒，前一秒才告诉下属要积极点哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717805}, {"id": 249633, "content": "“自卫”的时候，被老妈撞见????", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1129255}, {"id": 252707, "content": "装有男友，被问及细节生活问题瞬间暴露了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185588}, {"id": 251176, "content": "我以为我是其实不是", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195904}, {"id": 249641, "content": "时时刻刻都在崩塌，牺牲人设，换取平静，没什么不好，做事事周全的社会人太辛苦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263709}, {"id": 250155, "content": "有时候想扮演高冷结果成了傻子。\n出于嫉妒和攀比心理把自己的眉毛刮残。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1189760}, {"id": 249645, "content": "跟喜欢的人说话时牙上有菜", "image": "img/option/option/20171118091623CKRI6NBf5smx1urj", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1181539}, {"id": 250414, "content": "鬼畜歌单外放出声…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895450}, {"id": 249647, "content": "在夜店接到老爸电话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201097}, {"id": 250415, "content": "鬼畜歌单外放出声", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895450}, {"id": 249648, "content": "高中时候，大声讲骚话，被班主任听到，高冷形象瞬间消失?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103226}, {"id": 252721, "content": "开口人设即崩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1089723}, {"id": 258356, "content": "不存在的，我活得特别真实…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1232094}, {"id": 249910, "content": "鼻涕泡？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 497893}, {"id": 250678, "content": "一个认识的姐姐，四十多岁嫁给了一个大叔。姐姐平时瑜伽，恬静淡美，对大叔的咖啡事业很支持。突然有一天，姐姐在朋友圈说要去死，孩子谁能帮忙照顾？当时我看到朋友圈有点消化不动，怎么着就美好生活变得这么不堪重负了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191751}, {"id": 249655, "content": "段子手，八卦中心", "image": "img/option/option/20171118100158Ikg7MRQHF8sToUAt", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1160692}, {"id": 250168, "content": "本来是翩翩的古典钢琴气质女孩\n在合照时忽然摆出rapper的pose", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1189831}, {"id": 249659, "content": "减肥70斤算不算崩人设啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215386}, {"id": 249660, "content": "我也不知道自己有什么人设，包括别人。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186792}, {"id": 250941, "content": "蹦迪碰见辅导员，我的手还放在脱衣舞男的腹肌上", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192942}, {"id": 249662, "content": "说真的，人设不就是标签化的小名吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074638}, {"id": 248642, "content": "发朋友圈忘记分组，在deadline前的旅游照被老板看到，收到评价“勤奋努力的小黄原来也很贪玩嘛”", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 248643, "content": "恋爱初期在对象面前总保持一副贤良淑德的娇滴滴形象，有次素面朝天跟室友讲段子被看到，爽朗的哈哈声顿时凝固在空气中", "image": null, "praise_count": 214, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 248644, "content": "微博上不小心在一个美丽女孩照片下点到赞，高冷的老干部形象瞬时崩塌", "image": null, "praise_count": 124, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 249671, "content": "换新工作不到三个月，被同事一阳指：“啊？你竟然会说脏话？” ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536894}, {"id": 250183, "content": "帅哥形象因为痘印崩塌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1189914}, {"id": 249673, "content": "一直表现得很成熟稳重，直到有一天看动画片笑出?叫", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186401}, {"id": 249675, "content": "没有人设。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003128}, {"id": 250444, "content": "卧槽，两个字", "image": "img/option/option/20171122235420J6ghs8CovwzUQSGX", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895450}, {"id": 248654, "content": "恒源祥秋裤的快递包裹同事认出来，时尚达人的高大形象轰然倒塌", "image": null, "praise_count": 488, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 249679, "content": "在亲人面前一直是乖乖女，一次，妹妹去学校看我，住宿舍，我和室友侃大山，一时没控制，粗口爆出来，把妹妹吓着了", "image": "img/option/option/20171118143120aBymKFu1o8dNCegO", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186955}]}